overview: A tough, physical game of football gets these nine studs filled with testosterone and 'More Than Ready' for out-of-control, energized sex. Director Andrew Rosen tops all previous efforts to date giving you the 411 on the sexual aftermath of athletic exertion.
tagline: Daring Alex Graham makes a move on an sweaty Logan Vaughn, and when Bobby Clark listens in on an accidental call from them, he can't resist joining in.
title: More Than Ready
